document.section:
        Gauges


Gauges

All gauges are optional and may only be available if the XCSoar is
connected to a supported instrument.

\subsection{Variometer}

A needle-dial style display shows the variometer measurements.  The
gross variometer reading drives the main arrow on the dial, and in the
center of the dial the instantaneous measurement is written.
Additionally, speed command arrows appear above or below the gross
variometer measurement.

